+From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: herdr maintainers <maintainers@herdr.dev>
+Date: Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
+Subject: [PATCH] use controlled app-local ConPTY
+
+Never resolve a bare conpty.dll through the DLL search path. Use an approved
+app-local conpty.dll only when all OpenConsole architectures required by the
+application are deployed beside herdr.exe; otherwise retain the system
+implementation.
+
+Herdr issue: https://github.com/ogulcancelik/herdr/issues/761
+Vendored base: portable-pty 0.9.0
